# Agent Runner

<% if @error -%>
**Error reading agent-runner stats:** <%= @error %>
<% end -%>

## Service Status

<% if @runner_stats -%>
| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Active Tasks | <%= @runner_stats["activeTasks"] %> |
| Total Tasks Processed | <%= @runner_stats["totalTasksProcessed"] %> |
<% if @runner_stats["processedSinceStart"] -%>
<% counts = @runner_stats["processedSinceStart"] -%>
| Completed | <%= counts["completed"] || 0 %> |
| Failed | <%= counts["failed"] || 0 %> |
| Cancelled | <%= counts["cancelled"] || 0 %> |
<% end -%>
| Started At | <%= @runner_stats["startedAt"] %> |
| Last Task At | <%= @runner_stats["lastTaskAt"] || "None" %> |
| Last Completion At | <%= @runner_stats["lastCompletionAt"] || "None" %> |
| Last Failure At | <%= @runner_stats["lastFailureAt"] || "None" %> |
<% if @runner_stats["lastFailureReason"] -%>
| Last Failure | <%= @runner_stats["lastFailureReason"] %> |
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
**Agent runner is not reporting stats.** It may be offline or not yet started.
<% end -%>

## Redis Stream

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Stream Depth | <%= @runner_stats&.dig("streamDepth") || @stream_length %> |
| Pending Messages | <%= @runner_stats&.dig("streamPending") || @pending_count %> |

## Recent Task Runs
<% if @status_filter.present? -%>

Filtered by: **<%= @status_filter %>** ([show all](/system-admin/agent-runner))
<% end -%>

| ID | Agent | Status | Steps | Tokens | Started | Completed | Wait | Duration |
|----|-------|--------|-------|--------|---------|-----------|------|----------|
<% @recent_task_runs.each do |run| -%>
| [<%= run.id[0..7] %>](/system-admin/agent-runner/runs/<%= run.id %>) | <%= run.ai_agent&.name %> | <%= run.status %> | <%= run.steps_count %> | <%= run.total_tokens %> | <%= run.started_at&.strftime("%b %-d %H:%M:%S") %> | <%= run.completed_at&.strftime("%b %-d %H:%M:%S") %> | <%= run.formatted_queue_wait %> | <%= run.formatted_duration %> |
<% end -%>
